<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/238054-so-i-ve-read-this-book-and-reallllllyyyyy">So I&#39;ve read this book, and reallllllyyyyy liked it, but then i saw the next book was in a different perspective, and so i dont know if i should read the second book or not. Please help!?!!!!</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_238054'><a id="like_count_community_question_238054" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/238054?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">8 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F9565548-grave-mercy">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/238054-so-i-ve-read-this-book-and-reallllllyyyyy">7 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/238054-so-i-ve-read-this-book-and-reallllllyyyyy">See all 5 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
