<div id="review_2881281217" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2881281217" />
    <a title="Kayla Dawn" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/70522717-kayla-dawn"><img alt="Kayla Dawn" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1582845179p2/70522717.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2881281217?book_show_action=true">Jan 15, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Kayla Dawn" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Kayla Dawn" href="/user/show/70522717-kayla-dawn">Kayla Dawn</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9781783448234" href="/book/show/40242188-grave-mercy">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/70522717-kayla-dawn?shelf=owned-books">owned-books</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2881281217" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1955565055826978539">This was a pretty basic but decent YA fantasy story. <br/>Unfortunately a little too romance heavy for me but I liked the characters most of the time and I enjoyed the banter between Duval and Ismae. <br/>I hope I&apos;ll get a little more world building in the sequel!</span>
  <span id="freeText1955565055826978539" style="display:none">This was a pretty basic but decent YA fantasy story. <br />Unfortunately a little too romance heavy for me but I liked the characters most of the time and I enjoyed the banter between Duval and Ismae. <br />I hope I'll get a little more world building in the sequel!</span>
  <a data-text-id="1955565055826978539" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


