        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1488574437" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9054961172373407987"><b>3,5 stars</b><br/><br/><img src='https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1451663301ra/17573892.gif' width='330' height='220' alt='description' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/><br/>Such an interesting read.I love the story and the main character.Seems like a start to a great trilogy.I enjoyed reading about Ismae&apos;s adventures and I love how she developed as a character.There&apos;s action,there&apos;s a bit of slow-burning romance which I definitely liked,there&apos;s a lot of scheming and there are many interesting historical facts.The supporting characters are very interesting - Duval,the Duchess,Sybella etc.Yes,the writing and the world-building aren&apos;t perfect but I really con</span>
  <span id="freeText9054961172373407987" style="display:none"><b>3,5 stars</b><br><br><img src="https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1451663301ra/17573892.gif" width="330" height="220" alt="description" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br>Such an interesting read.I love the story and the main character.Seems like a start to a great trilogy.I enjoyed reading about Ismae's adventures and I love how she developed as a character.There's action,there's a bit of slow-burning romance which I definitely liked,there's a lot of scheming and there are many interesting historical facts.The supporting characters are very interesting - Duval,the Duchess,Sybella etc.Yes,the writing and the world-building aren't perfect but I really connected with these characters and I had a great time reading about them.Plus,the story really is unique and captivating. The Duchess seriously needs the Lord's help,though,she's in a difficult position. A really good book with a lot of potential.</span>
  <a data-text-id="9054961172373407987" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


